## Useful commands reminder

- build

`podman build --build-arg GIT_HASH="$(git rev-parse HEAD)" -t helix:latest .`

- run interactively:

`podman run -ti --rm --volume /home/kzm/Desktop/Current/TestsContainer:/home/ubuntu/host_mountpoint --name helix_test localhost/helix:latest`

- prune:

`podman container prune`

- inspect:

`podman inspect localhost/helix:latest | grep GIT`
